In 1968, Andriyashik et al.21 detected two exciton peaks in the absorption spectrum of bulk InSe, which they ascribed to the ground and first excited states. They derived the direct energy gap Eg≃1.36eV\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
